title: Bug 121687: Exception thrown when exporting data in table within a grid cell
OB: When trying to export data in a table that is placed inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
EB: The export process for tables within grid cells should be successfully executed without any exceptions.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Insert a table into one grid cell. 2. Insert another table into another grid cell. 3. Attempt to export the data in the tables.
